rvices in domestic market.\",\"mainPatentEN\":\"\",\"activityTwoCN\":\"\",\"employee\":\"71\",\"mainBrandCN\":\"3ACredit,3AVerify,3ACollect\",\"mainPatentCN\":\"\",\"mainProductCN\":\"中国商业信用报告、国际商业信用报告、实地认证、电话认证、消费者信用评估、商业信用评估、应收账审计、企业商账催收、金融机构账务催收、商业信息研究、商业法律顾问、全球法律援助、企业信用咨询等。\",\"saleDomesticCN\":\"该公司61%的产品在国内市场上销售。\",\"activityOneEN\":\"Credit and risk management support services\",\"activityOneCN\":\"商业信用及风险管理\",\"exportAreaEN\":\"\",\"exportAreaCN\":\"\",\"enterprisescale\":\"中小型企业\",\"productionEN\":\"Subject has an annual sales of about 70,000 credit reports.\",\"imports\":\"19\",\"purchaseTermEN\":\"various payment methods, with settlement according to the contract\",\"saleTermCN\":\"多种支付方式，按合同结算。\",\"productionCN\":\"该公司年销售报告7万份。\",\"saleTermEN\":\"various payment methods, with settlement according to the contract\",\"purchaseDomesticEN\":\"Subject sources 81% of its products from domestic market.\",\"purchaseInternationlEN\":\"Subject sources 19% of its products from overseas market, mainly Europe and America, Asia, Africa.\",\"mainProductEN\":\"Chinese business credit reports, international business credit reports, location verification, telephone verification, consumer credit assessment, commercial credit assessment, receivable auditing, commercial debt collection, financing institution debt collection, business information research, commercial legal adviser, global legal aid, enterprise credit consulting, etc.\",\"purchaseDomesticCN\":\"该公司的产品81%从国内采购。\",\"purchaseTermCN\":\"多种支付方式，按合同结算。\",\"activityThreeCN\":\"\",\"activityThreeEN\":\"\",\"purchaseInternationlCN\":\"该公司的产品19%从海外进口，主要在欧美、亚洲、非洲等地。\",\"certificationEN\":\"Subject has foreign-related investigation license.\\r\\nSubject has obtained the enterprise credit business operating license issued by the central bank.\",\"discription_web\":\"\",\"infoCN\":\"公司是全球组织，Creditreform，的成员之一。Creditreform成立于1879年，它的总部设在德国诺伊斯。Creditreform International 是一个在欧洲23个国家有独立实体的国际机构。它是全球知名的重要信息提供者，在欧洲拥有超过167个办事处，现在随着跟商安信对齐，也在中国有办事处。\\r\\n\\r\\n公司拥有欧洲最大的信用信息服务机构Creditreform的SI信用风险评估体系的全面技术支持，可使用全球24个国家超过6,000万家企业的信用数据资源。\\r\\n\\r\\n合作伙伴：Creditreform、Anzen、Bierens、EIA-global、ABC-Amega。\",\"premiseEN\":\"Subject is currently operating at the above stated address.\",\"ownership\":\"租用\",\"size\":\"1800\",\"premiseCN\":\"该公司目前在首页所述之地址办公。\",\"certificationCN\":\"该公司拥有涉外调查许可证。\\r\\n该公司获得央行颁发的企业征信业务经营备案证。                 \",\"locationEN\":\"Subject is located in Shanghai Mobile Internet Innovation Industrial Park which is the landmark building of Baoshan District, Shanghai.\",\"importAreaCN\":\"欧美、亚洲、非洲\",\"saleInternationlCN\":\"该公司39%的产品出口海外市场。\",\"saleInternationlEN\":\"Subject sells 39% of its services to overseas market.\\r\\n\",\"infoEN\":\"Subject is a part of the Creditreform global organization. Headquartered in Neuss, Germany it was founded in 1879. Creditreform International is an association of independent Creditreform entities with country offices in 23 European countries. It is globally known as one of the more significant information providers with more than 167 offices throughout Europe and now, with its alignment with 3ACredit, also in China.\\r\\n\\r\\nSubject has the full support of Europe\'s largest credit information agency, Creditreform\'s, Solvency index credint risk assessment system, and can use the credit data resources of more than 60 million enterprises in 24 countries around the world.\\r\\n\\r\\nSubject\'s business partners: Creditreform, Amazon, Bierens, EIA-global and ABC-Amega.\",\"importAreaEN\":\"Europe and America, Asia, Africa\"},\"empLoyee_2\":\"2015:  64\"}', null, null, '9364590846', '是');

